1. Go to virtualenv directory
($cd gest)=>if virtualenv directory name is "gest"
2. $source bin/activate
3. $FLASK_APP=predict_all_gpu.py
(Put "predict_all_gpu.py" file in gest/ directory)
4. $flask run --host=0.0.0.0
5. Open all_gpu_final.html in chrome
6. Click on start button to start the prediction.
7. Keep the gesture for at least 5 secs in rectangular box.
8. When you do the gesture for space then Word will be printed in the textarea below label WORD on webapp.


NOTE : j and z are excluded while training as they are dynamic gestures and cant be trained with static gestures.
